-- China Mobile's Sichuan General Manager Was Detained June 25, Caixin Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-30T03:56:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/china-mobile-s-sichuan-general-manager-was-detained-june-25-caixin-says.html

          
          
             The general manager of  China Mobile
Ltd. ’s Sichuan unit was detained on June 25 as part of an
investigation of a “personal economic problem,” Caixin Online
 reported today , citing an unidentified person at the company.  
 Zhao Yi, a Beijing-based spokesman for China Mobile, said
he was “unaware” of the issue.  
